This list includes properties and districts listed on the [National Register of Historic Places](/National_Register_of_Historic_Places) in [Beaufort County, North Carolina](/Beaufort_County,_North_Carolina). For those who appreciate the bureaucratic beauty of preservation, or perhaps just enjoy a good historical scavenger hunt, this compilation serves as a comprehensive guide. One can almost feel the weight of history emanating from these documented sites, a stark contrast to the fleeting nature of most human endeavors. Click the "Map of all coordinates" link to the right to view an online map of all properties and districts with latitude and longitude coordinates in the table below. It's a rather neat way to visualize where these relics of the past are stubbornly holding their ground. [1]

This [National Park Service](/National_Park_Service) list, a testament to enduring federal commitment, is complete through NPS recent listings posted December 12, 2025. One can only assume they're still adding entries even as the world around them changes. [2]

